<img src="https://i0.wp.com/837274.smushcdn.com/1798008/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Edem-Mood-Swing-Ep.jpg?ssl=1" alt="Edem Recruits Darkovibes, Kelvynboy &amp; Efya For His New EP &quot;Mood Swings&quot;" data-recalc-dims="1" /> Mood Swings cover artwork Multiple award winning Ghanaian rapper Edem drops his much anticipated EP, titled "Mood Swings". "Mood Swings" is a 6 track EP from the VRMG boss, with features by Darkovibes, Kelvynboy, and Efya. The EP is an audiovisual project, with each song being depicted by a specific color in the official videos. The visuals depicts Edem explaining his mood in a cinematic way. Beautifully representing each mood with a color, the songs on the EP, from “Love You”, “Kpo”, “Money”, “Efo Kojo”, “In Ghana” and “Chidi”, colourfully comes together as an embodiment of whom Edem is. To Edem, "Mood Swings" will allow the world to see him through the various musical lenses as an artist. He is also hopeful that each song will be heard and appreciated for what it is and what it means to him. Speaking on the EP, Edem commented: “It is all the colors that come together for you to see the rainbow, and the rainbow is the representation of the brighter side of life. The synergy is in all the moods coming together”. Stream the project below. Let us know what you think in the comments! RELATED: Edem ft. Davido – Toto (Remix) STREAM ON DSPs The post Edem Recruits Darkovibes, Kelvynboy & Efya For His New EP "Mood Swings" appeared first on Latest Naija Nigerian Music, Songs & Video – Notjustok. Original Article Get all the Latest news, Breaking headlines,Sport, Education, Finance, Gists, Jobs, Music/Video, Technology and Top stories in real time in Nigeria and around the world.